title: ISurfaceExtendFeatureData.IGetItems
description: Gets the extended faces and edges for this surface-extend feature.
returns: in-process, unmanaged C++: Pointer to an array extended items ( faces and edges ) of size Count VBA, VB.NET, C#, and C++/CLI: Not supported See In-process Methods for details about this type of method.
remarks:
Call
ISurfaceExtendFeatureData::GetItemsCount
before calling this method.
See
Accessing Selections that Define Features
for additional details.
